{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Game Controller framework enables games to integrate with MFi game controllers and take advantage of exciting new modes of input. Check out the latest additions and get expert advice about best practices to follow when adding game controller support to your titles. Understand how to avoid common pitfalls and gain key insights into what it takes to create an experience that’s intuitive and fun."}],"metadata":{"title":"Designing for Game Controllers","roleHeading":"WWDC14","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"role":"sampleCode"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc14-611-designing-for-game-controllers"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Be the hero to change that by reading the transcript and providing notes! It’s super easy:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC14"]]},"sections":[],"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"overridingTitle":"Read Transcript","isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2014\/611\/"}},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC14-611-Designing-for-Game-Controllers","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"https://wwdcnotes.com/documentation/wwdcnotes/contributing":{"titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Learn More…","type":"text"}],"title":"Learn More…","type":"link","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/co